</script>
</div></div></div></div></div><div class="actions-region"><div class="panel-pane pane-custom-pagers-pane" ><div class="pane-content"><ul class="custom-pager custom-pager-bottom"><li class="previous"> <span class="custom-pager-title">Previous</span> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span> <a href="/articles/interviews/smart-materials-promise-long-term-road-repairs">Smart materials promise long term road repairs</a></li><li class="next"> <span class="custom-pager-title">Next</span> <a href="/articles/interviews/was-charles-darwin-lucky-love">Was Charles Darwin lucky in love?</a> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-podcasts-panel-pane-3" ><h2 class="pane-title"> Related Content</h2><div class="pane-content"><div class="view view-podcasts view-id-podcasts view-display-id-panel_pane_3 view-dom-id-a8cc65381aa147d781ecbfa2c366cce1"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/articles/interviews/medicine">Medicine</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="/articles/interviews/genetic-reason-high-rates-ms-northern-europe" class="ajax-exclude">The genetic reason for high rates of MS in Northern Europe</a></h4></div></div><div class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/podcasts/short">In Short</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="/podcasts/short/ancient-dna-extracted-cave-dirt" class="ajax-exclude">Ancient DNA extracted from cave dirt</a></h4></div></div><div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/articles